name: Liquid Reflections #8
description: The last artwork of Liquid Reflections Series wss released for the third OBJKT4OBJKT Event. This series examines the possibilities of using liquid forms and symmetry to create abstract images. Each image is a fight between order and chaos, where order imposed by the symmetry clashes with the fluidity of colours that cannot be contained in their boundaries. It is a fight of contradicting forces that govern our lives. Series consists of 8 artworks, each work is 4000x4000 pixels.
